0.Name: Vendas
0.SqlCommand:
with 
\tpdv as (
\t\tselect  obj.id, obj.name, obj.integrationid 
\t\tfrom finance.financeunitgroup obj
\t\tleft join mobiage.pdv as pdvfm on pdvfm.id=obj.id
\t\twhere obj.id='{idpdv}'
\t\t),
\t\t
\tpdvaberturasefechamentos as (
\t\tselect pdv.id,pdv.name,pdv.integrationid, cashcheckin.id, cashcheckin.oi, 
\t\t\tcashcheckin.id as idAbertura, cashcheckin.date as abertura, cashcheckout.id as idFechamento, 
\t\t\tcashcheckout.date as fechamento, cashcheckin.status, cashcheckin.employee_id, pessoa.name as nomefuncionario, 
\t\t\tpessoa.secundaryname, pessoa.securitylogin, cashcheckin.group_id, cashcheckin.change 
\t\tfrom finance.cashcheckin as cashcheckin   
\t\tinner join pdv as pdv on cashcheckin.group_id=pdv.id
\t\tleft join finance.cashcheckin_cashcheckout as cashcheckin_cashcheckout on cashcheckin_cashcheckout.cashcheckin_id = cashcheckin.id
\t\tleft join finance.cashcheckout as cashcheckout on  cashcheckout.id = cashcheckin_cashcheckout.cashcheckouts_id
\t\tleft join finance.individual as pessoa on pessoa.id = cashcheckin.employee_id
\t\twhere cashcheckin.group_id ='{idpdv}' and cashcheckin.id = '{idcheckin}'
\t\t),
\t\t
\tvendas as (
\t\tselect  movementgroup.id as idvenda, movementgroup.oi, movementgroup.pdv_id, movementgroup.count as QtdItens, 
\t\t\tmovementgroup.movementdate as data, movementgroup.sequencialcode as numeropedido, movementgroup.status, 
\t\t\tmovementgroup.subtotal, movementgroup.valuediscount as valordesconto, movementgroup.total, movementgroup.operationtype_id, 
\t\t\tmovementgroup.targetperson_id as vendedor, movementgroup.associatedmovement_id, 
\t\t\tmovementgroup.responsable_id as cliente,pessoafm.name
\t\tfrom mobiage.movementgroup as movementgroup 
\t\tinner join pdv as pdv on movementgroup.pdv_id=pdv.integrationid   
\t\tinner join pdvaberturasefechamentos as pdvaberturasefechamentos on pdv.id = pdvaberturasefechamentos.group_id
\t\tinner join mobiage.person as pessoafm on movementgroup.responsable_id=pessoafm.id
\t\tleft  join mobiage.movementgroup as mvorigem on mvorigem.associatedmovement_id = movementgroup.id
\t\t
\t\twhere (movementgroup.status = 'FINISH' and mvorigem.id IS NULL ) 
\t\tand (
\t\t\t(pdvaberturasefechamentos.fechamento IS NOT NULL and (movementgroup.movementdate between pdvaberturasefechamentos.abertura and pdvaberturasefechamentos.fechamento)) 
\t\tor (pdvaberturasefechamentos.fechamento IS NULL and movementgroup.movementdate > pdvaberturasefechamentos.abertura ))
\t\t)
\t\t\t
\t\tselect vendas.* from vendas

2.Name: UnidadesFinanceira
2.SqlCommand:
with 
\tpdv as (
\t\tselect  obj.id, obj.name, obj.integrationid 
\t\tfrom finance.financeunitgroup obj
\t\tleft join mobiage.pdv as pdvfm on pdvfm.id=obj.id
\t\twhere obj.id=962 
\t\t),
\t\t
\tpdvaberturasefechamentos as (
\t\tselect pdv.id,pdv.name,pdv.integrationid, cashcheckin.id, cashcheckin.oi, 
\t\t\tcashcheckin.id as idAbertura, cashcheckin.date as abertura, cashcheckout.id as idFechamento, 
\t\t\tcashcheckout.date as fechamento, cashcheckin.status, cashcheckin.employee_id, pessoa.name as nomefuncionario, 
\t\t\tpessoa.secundaryname, pessoa.securitylogin, cashcheckin.group_id, cashcheckin.change 
\t\tfrom finance.cashcheckin as cashcheckin   
\t\tinner join pdv as pdv on cashcheckin.group_id=pdv.id
\t\tleft join finance.cashcheckin_cashcheckout as cashcheckin_cashcheckout on cashcheckin_cashcheckout.cashcheckin_id = cashcheckin.id
\t\tleft join finance.cashcheckout as cashcheckout on  cashcheckout.id = cashcheckin_cashcheckout.cashcheckouts_id
\t\tleft join finance.individual as pessoa on pessoa.id = cashcheckin.employee_id
\t\twhere cashcheckin.group_id = 962  and cashcheckin.id = '{idcheckin}' 
\t\t),

\tunidfin as( select uf.dtype, uf.name, sum(mov.total) 
\t\tfrom mobiage.movementgroup mov
\t\tinner join finance.title tit on (mov.id = tit.idintegracao)
\t\tinner join finance.titleparcel tp on (tp.title_id = tit.id)
\t\tinner join finance.parcelpayment prpg on (prpg.parcel_id = tp.id)
\t\tinner join finance.payment pgto on (pgto.id=prpg.payment_id)
\t\tinner join finance.entry entra on (entra.payment_id=pgto.id)
\t\tinner join finance.financeunit uf on (uf.id=entra.financeunit_id)
\t\tinner join pdv as pdv on mov.pdv_id=pdv.integrationid   
\t\tinner join pdvaberturasefechamentos as pdvaberturasefechamentos on pdv.id = pdvaberturasefechamentos.group_id
\t\tleft  join mobiage.movementgroup as mvorigem on mvorigem.associatedmovement_id = mov.id\t\t
\t\twhere (mov.status = 'FINISH' and mvorigem.id  IS NULL ) 
\t\t\tand ((pdvaberturasefechamentos.fechamento IS NOT NULL and (mov.movementdate between pdvaberturasefechamentos.abertura and pdvaberturasefechamentos.fechamento)) 
\t\t\tor (pdvaberturasefechamentos.fechamento IS NULL and mov.movementdate > pdvaberturasefechamentos.abertura ))
\t\tgroup by 1,2)
\tselect * from unidfin \t

\t\tand (
\t\t\t(pdvaberturasefechamentos.fechamento IS NOT NULL and (movementgroup.movementdate between pdvaberturasefechamentos.abertura and pdvaberturasefechamentos.fechamento)) 
\t\tor (pdvaberturasefechamentos.fechamento IS NULL and movementgroup.movementdate > pdvaberturasefechamentos.abertura ))
\t\t)
